@page "/aboutus"

<div class="about-us">
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header class="header-section">
        <div>
            <img src="images/about_us_logo.png" alt="Giveaway Image" class="intro-image">
        </div>
        <h1 class="header-title">TO WIN A GIVEAWAY TODAY</h1>
        <p class="header-subtitle">All you have to do is Play!</p>
    </header>

    <!-- Introduction Section -->
    <section class="introduction-section" style="background-color: #f9f9f9; padding: 40px; text-align: center;">
        <div class="intro-content" style="max-width: 800px; margin: auto;">
            <div class="intro-text">
                <h2 style="color: #2b7a78; font-size: 2.5rem; font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;">Welcome to JusGiveaway!</h2>
                <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #4a4a4a; line-height: 1.8;">
                    JusGiveaway merges technology with philanthropy thereby creating a space where generosity meets fun
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #4a4a4a; line-height: 1.8;">
                    We live in a world where many want to make an impact, support a cause, add value and give back to communities and so we have created JusGiveaway, a platform where giveaways can be done by hosting fun games thereby bringing a playful twist to giving.
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #4a4a4a; line-height: 1.8;">
                    We know there are many who want to give back to their communities and jusgivesway.com exists to make this possible.
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #4a4a4a; line-height: 1.8;">
                    We host original and customized games for individuals and groups who want to do giveaways. We also curate games for conferences and events to make them fun.
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #4a4a4a; line-height: 1.8;">
                    This is the first of many to come and so we want to ask you, will you give back and make it fun?
                </p>
                <p style="font-size: 1.25rem; color: #4a4a4a; line-height: 1.8;">
                    Contact us at <a href="mailto:jusgiveaway.dbf@gmail.com" style="color: #2b7a78; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none;">jusgiveaway.dbf@gmail.com</a> and we’ll make it happen.
                </p>

                <a href="#" class="cta-button" style="display: inline-block; background-color: #3da9fc; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 5px; text-decoration: none;">Follow us on Instagram</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>
